[Name] LibISOfs
[Summary] A library to pack up hard disk files and directories into a ISO 9660 disk image.
[Description] libisofs is a library to create an ISO-9660 filesystem, and supports extensions like RockRidge or Joliet. It is also a full featured ISO-9660 editor, allowing you to modify an ISO image or multisession disc, including file addition and removal, change of file names and attributes, etc
[License] GNU General Public License version 2 
[Homepage] http://libburnia-project.org/wiki/Libisofs
